Hi,

Thanks to Niels & Corinne for the edited version.  I am still in the
process of reading the revision.

I too am inclined to start the RGLC real soon now, but wanted to give
people a chance to read and comment first.  Plan to take some sort of
action next week on this. I tend to believe that this is not something
